WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:05.119
Hey, good morning family. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:05.120 --> 00:00:10.923
Well, there is a lot going on right now, isn't there, baby? A major earthquake took place in Thailand, 7.7.

00:00:10.924 --> 00:00:15.992
And so far, they say 100,000 people they think have perished.

00:00:15.993 --> 00:00:18.728
There's rubble on everybody. So, we need to pray for them today.

00:00:18.729 --> 00:00:25.992
That's one of the things we're going to lift up: that they would find the survivors and help find them quickly.

00:00:25.993 --> 00:00:30.729
You know, there are people buried underneath that rubble and all the debris.

00:00:30.730 --> 00:00:40.972
And I'm praying that they'll have rescue dogs, whatever they have, to find these people that are still alive, and that the people that are alive will be safe wherever they're at.

00:00:40.973 --> 00:00:49.485
This is a very, very serious situation. And you know, y'all, a lot of people say, 'Hey, Brandon, you prophesied.'Yes, I talked about this.

00:00:49.486 --> 00:00:53.428
This is what the Lord showed me was coming back a couple weeks ago.

00:00:53.429 --> 00:01:01.270
And he told us, he said, 'Great earthquakes were going to start to take place. As labor pains upon a woman, so will it be.

00:01:01.271 --> 00:01:07.262
We're seeing the labor pains intensify.'And he told me they were going to intensify, folks.

00:01:07.263 --> 00:01:35.085
And he said, 'Now, when I told you all we prayed last time, I saw that you could not go horizontal in your eyes in the flesh because of what we're going to see.'Because in the natural, if you are looking at what I have seen coming, if you're looking at going horizontal, it will have the tendency to try to get you in fear because of what we're going to see, because so many things are going to start to escalate.

00:01:35.086 --> 00:01:44.092
And he told us major earthquakes were going to start to take place. Major. And it would not be these little 5.0 earthquakes.

00:01:44.093 --> 00:02:04.654
I saw great earthquakes that would start to take place and they would happen in the sea, and I saw the sea opening and I saw the gases coming up and I saw the deep-sea fish—this would be a major sign that when we would see fish we've never seen before.

00:02:04.655 --> 00:02:26.441
Signs of fish that we've never seen before dying and washing up on the shore or fleeing the area and coming up higher out of the deep waters, trying to get away from what's happening on the ocean floor, because the Lord showed me there would be major things taking place on the ocean floor.

00:02:26.442 --> 00:02:34.104
And I saw tsunamis. I saw the one going into Alaska again. I saw that one.

00:02:34.105 --> 00:02:37.924
I've told you all about that. I told you all about the ones taking place in Japan.

00:02:37.925 --> 00:02:44.292
I've told you about the earthquakes in a lot of places, but it was more than that. It was about volcanoes.

00:02:44.293 --> 00:02:52.403
And I warned you about Italy and a major earthquake taking place in Italy and a tsunami wave coming in there.

00:02:52.404 --> 00:03:00.360
And so, like I said, for all the things and all the warnings that I'm warning you all about, he said this was not something that was man.

00:03:00.361 --> 00:03:06.318
This part was not something man-made. It's the earth groaning. It's the earth shaking.

00:03:06.319 --> 00:03:11.377
There's going to be major things happening in the earth because it is having birth pains.

00:03:11.378 --> 00:03:15.913
And we're going to see it because why? Jesus Christ is coming. Bottom line.

00:03:15.914 --> 00:03:20.157
And we're getting ready to step into the tribulation period.

00:03:20.158 --> 00:03:27.913
I believe the rapture of the church is right at our doorstep and most people are still asleep.

00:03:27.914 --> 00:03:37.163
And that's why he told us, not last prayer or the prayer before, whatever it was, he said, 'I'm going for the ones in the backfield.

00:03:37.164 --> 00:03:46.624
I'm coming for the revival for the ones in the backfield.'Brandon, I'm leaving the ninety-nine to go after the one.

00:03:46.625 --> 00:03:54.900
And most people are going, 'Brandon, really?'No. Seriously, God loves you and he's coming after you.

00:03:54.901 --> 00:03:59.650
He said, 'Satan has come after the kids, but Brandon, I'm coming after him harder.

00:03:59.651 --> 00:04:06.719
I'm coming after this youth generation. I'm coming after the ones that seem like there was no hope.

00:04:06.720 --> 00:04:13.385
I'm coming after the unlovely.'Do you understand, folks? God is a God that is not a loser.

00:04:13.386 --> 00:04:19.995
He's a victorious God. And we are on the victory side. And I'm telling you, God is coming after your unsaved loved ones.

00:04:19.996 --> 00:04:23.891
And they're going to have that road to Damascus experience.

00:04:23.892 --> 00:04:31.758
They're going to have that shaking to awaken. And I believe we're not going to go in the rapture defeated.

00:04:31.759 --> 00:04:34.895
We're going victorious and we're going without spot or wrinkle.

00:04:34.896 --> 00:04:42.336
And we're going to go with the healing revival and demonstrations and manifestations of the glory of God like we've never seen before.

00:04:42.337 --> 00:04:47.486
But yes, we are going to see. I told you it's like focusing on a quarter. There's two sides.

00:04:47.487 --> 00:04:55.070
The quarter is really thin, but both sides are very different from the other. And that's the way it's going to be.

00:04:55.071 --> 00:05:01.728
You're going to either focus on the light or you're going to focus on the darkness because things are going to go gross darkness.

00:05:01.729 --> 00:05:10.319
So much so, the darkness that I saw that was coming was so dark that it was tangible.

00:05:10.320 --> 00:05:16.413
It was just like it was in Egypt. Darkness that you could feel.

00:05:16.414 --> 00:05:21.492
I don't know about you, but I've never felt darkness so dark that you can feel it.

00:05:21.493 --> 00:05:30.055
How do you—I mean, that is overwhelming darkness. The light's going to get lighter and the dark's going to get darker.

00:05:30.056 --> 00:05:36.788
But the glorious church is going to rise up like the Tommy Hicks vision.

00:05:36.789 --> 00:05:44.281
And I believe like Jesus said to us in the last two or three prayer times ago: 'Who's going to say yes?

00:05:44.282 --> 00:05:52.437
Who's going to say yes?'So here we see another thing: Zelensky saying, 'We're not going to forgive the United States.

00:05:52.438 --> 00:05:58.008
We're not going to pay back the United States debts.'And we see him saying, 'We want aid.

00:05:58.009 --> 00:06:06.598
We want more missiles. We want this stuff.'And I said, I told you all there will be—that man is a very dark man.

00:06:06.599 --> 00:06:12.130
And I'm telling you, there's going to be a false—I feel it in my spirit still. I'm still praying over this.

00:06:12.131 --> 00:06:22.007
And it's something we all should be praying over: a false flag event, a provoking of trying to poke the bear.

00:06:22.008 --> 00:06:30.323
I'm telling you all, we need to be praying that they don't try to poke the bear—poking the bear to do something very drastic.

00:06:30.324 --> 00:06:43.638
And I said there is a distraction over here while the Houthis and all this stuff going on for what Iran is not wanting to be uncovered. And there will be an uncovering.

00:06:43.639 --> 00:07:03.443
And I've seen the United States of America striking Iran, Israel striking Iran, and it brought on great anti-Semitism, more than what we've ever seen before in America, protesting the lives that they'd say were taken in Iran in the days ahead.

00:07:03.444 --> 00:07:22.666
A major escalation of war in the Middle East for what I have seen coming with Turkey going alongside Syria in the days ahead and them trying to basically be like a big brother to Syria more than what we've ever seen before.

00:07:22.667 --> 00:07:28.092
Then we will see—I've seen in the spirit more about Iran. So we'll see.

00:07:28.093 --> 00:07:32.474
We're praying over that stuff. So we pray that it does not happen.

00:07:32.475 --> 00:07:39.250
But I'm telling you, we will see an increase of war and rumors of war in these days ahead.

00:07:39.251 --> 00:07:45.345
And we are going to see plagues, pestilence, and we're going to see these things, folks.

00:07:45.346 --> 00:07:53.092
The Bible said we would. The Bible said we would. But where are we supposed to keep our eyes?

00:07:53.093 --> 00:07:59.350
On him. Yep. Why? Because our redemption's drawing nigh. And he said to be hearing him.

00:07:59.351 --> 00:08:05.806
If you are not listening to the Lord, you could go in the wrong place at the wrong time and not make it.

00:08:05.807 --> 00:08:11.119
But if you are following the Holy Spirit like a snapping of a finger, boom, boom, boom.

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:18.305
And you're listening to him, being filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit, you will always be protected. You are his beloved.

00:08:18.306 --> 00:08:30.389
But if you step out of sync with him, it's an opportunity for the devil to try to take you out before you're supposed to go home. And I refuse to let the devil do that.

00:08:30.390 --> 00:08:44.373
We are going to be in sync with the Father, listening to his voice and the stranger's voice we will not follow, and being like that heartbeat, following as he dances, as he leads in prayer, we will follow.

00:08:44.374 --> 00:08:48.405
But we're seeing the things happen on the news is what I'm trying to tell you.

00:08:48.406 --> 00:08:55.735
We had the first major earthquake and 100,000 people. That's terrible.

00:08:55.736 --> 00:09:01.353
We pray for the victims. We pray for the people. But I'm telling you, there's more coming.

00:09:01.354 --> 00:09:13.324
And it will happen with the oceans. We know that we are looking because we know our redemption is drawing nigh.

00:09:13.325 --> 00:09:19.596
We're looking to the skies. But this is what I saw in prayer yesterday.

00:09:19.597 --> 00:09:26.228
I saw Jesus standing right here and he was looking at a brook.

00:09:26.229 --> 00:09:34.049
It was a stream and there were mountains on this side like a valley.

00:09:34.050 --> 00:09:42.836
I could see rock ledges and there was a stream running through like a snake stream.

00:09:42.837 --> 00:09:47.596
It looked like it was curvy and it ran through, and Jesus was watching.

00:09:47.597 --> 00:09:55.625
I saw people on both sides come up to the water and start lapping up the water.

00:09:55.626 --> 00:10:00.757
Some of them were very dignified in the way they got on their knees.

00:10:00.758 --> 00:10:07.554
They had their nice clothes on and they didn't want to look like they were going to dirty themselves.

00:10:07.555 --> 00:10:13.591
They got up there and they just barely squatted down and they cupped their hands and they brought the water up to them.

00:10:13.592 --> 00:10:21.976
But some of the people that went up to the water were desperate and they were just like, 'I am so thirsty.

00:10:21.977 --> 00:10:31.359
I have to have this water.'And they were undignified. They did not look like they had a lot going for them.

00:10:31.360 --> 00:10:37.022
Their clothes weren't as nice. They didn't look like they were real clean.

00:10:37.023 --> 00:10:43.793
They were desperate and out of the desperation they were drinking the water.

00:10:43.794 --> 00:10:49.643
They were trying to fill themselves up with that water all they could as fast as they could.

00:10:49.644 --> 00:10:57.398
You knew the other people were desperate and thirsty but they didn't want to display themselves like that.

00:10:57.399 --> 00:11:05.912
I saw the Lord and I said, 'Lord, what are you doing in my prayer time yesterday?'and he said, 'I'm watching to see who's the thirstiest.

00:11:05.913 --> 00:11:12.554
I'm watching to see who's going to come with me to the greater glory. Who can be used for the greater glory?

00:11:12.555 --> 00:11:23.762
I'm watching how they're drinking.'So, this is the scripture the Lord gave to me when I was in the vision.

00:11:23.763 --> 00:11:28.116
Diana's going to read this and then we're going to go to another scripture the Lord gave me.

00:11:28.117 --> 00:11:34.068
And the Lord said to Gideon, 'The men are still too many. Bring them down to the water and I will test them for you there.

00:11:34.069 --> 00:11:38.077
And he of whom I say to you, 'This man shall go with you,'shall go with you.

00:11:38.078 --> 00:11:43.696
And he of whom I say to you, 'This man shall not go with you,'shall not go.'So he brought the men down to the water.

00:11:43.697 --> 00:11:50.582
And the Lord said to Gideon, 'Everyone who laps up the water with his tongue as a dog laps it, you shall set by himself.

00:11:50.583 --> 00:11:58.319
Likewise, everyone who bows down on his knees to drink.'And the number of those who lapped, putting their hand to their mouth, was 300 men.

00:11:58.320 --> 00:12:02.809
But the rest of the people bowed down upon their knees to drink the water.

00:12:02.810 --> 00:12:09.367
And the Lord said to Gideon, 'With the 300 men who lapped, I will deliver you and give the Midianites into your hand.

00:12:09.368 --> 00:12:20.638
Let all the others return every man to his home.'So basically, he was looking for the people who were undignified.

00:12:20.639 --> 00:12:25.186
He was looking for the people who were sold out and were really thirsty.

00:12:25.187 --> 00:12:31.759
They did not care about how they looked. They probably looked really dumb.

00:12:31.760 --> 00:12:43.413
They probably didn't look too educated. They just wanted the water. How desperate do you want the water?

00:12:43.414 --> 00:12:57.599
And the Lord said to me, 'I'm watching to see how my people are drinking to see the ones who I'm going to be able to take to the end-time glory.

00:12:57.600 --> 00:13:12.616
Who are the ones and how are they drinking? Do they care about what they look like?

00:13:12.617 --> 00:13:24.328
Are they sold out? Are they all in? Are they too worried about how they look in public? Or will I look embarrassed if I lay hands on the sick?

00:13:24.329 --> 00:13:36.822
And if he asks me to cast out a devil, is it convenient for me right now because that person over there might talk bad about me?

00:13:36.823 --> 00:13:46.220
I'm all in and I'm drinking that water with all I've got because I'm desperate just to please him.

00:13:46.221 --> 00:14:08.208
No matter what nobody else thinks, I am going to lap it up like a dog.'He just took 300. So, it doesn't take a lot for this end-time harvest.

00:14:08.209 --> 00:14:15.198
He's just looking for the ones who don't care about what everybody else thinks about them.

00:14:15.199 --> 00:14:29.823
He's just wanting somebody that wants just to drink. How desperate are you for the water? How thirsty? How hungry? That's what it's coming down to.

00:14:29.824 --> 00:14:38.202
Gideon's mighty men, the ones that went and defeated, were just sold out and they looked foolish.

00:14:38.203 --> 00:14:51.119
But God said, 'He's the one; you can use them.'The other guys are too dignified.

00:14:51.120 --> 00:15:07.397
So this is another scripture that we got about the drinking, letting the Holy Spirit use you. It's in John 7.

00:15:07.398 --> 00:15:18.118
Now on the final and most important day of the feast, Jesus stood and he cried in a loud voice, 'If any man is thirsty, let him come to me and drink.

00:15:18.119 --> 00:15:47.975
He who believes in me, who cleaves to and trusts in and relies on me, as the scripture has said, from his innermost being shall flow continuously springs and rivers of living water.'He who believes in me, who cleaves to and trusts in and relies on me.

00:15:47.976 --> 00:16:02.159
Cleaves to, trusts in, and relies on me. As the scripture has said, from his innermost being shall flow continuously springs and rivers of living water.

00:16:02.160 --> 00:16:09.580
Springs and rivers of living water that are coming out of the throne.

00:16:09.581 --> 00:16:16.924
And he's watching to see how you drink. This scripture right here is what he showed me.

00:16:16.925 --> 00:16:23.198
This is John 7, which is amazing. It goes along with Gideon and with the drinking.

00:16:23.199 --> 00:16:38.763
When you're praying in the spirit, you're coming to him for the drink. And as you're drinking from him, out of you flow the rivers.

00:16:38.764 --> 00:16:44.893
We're trying to dump that river out on everybody else because it's the anointing that destroys the yoke.

00:16:44.894 --> 00:17:03.100
But a lot of people go up to the river with a little straw and they try to drink with a little straw, filling themselves up, but they're trying to dump a bathtub outside of you.

00:17:03.101 --> 00:17:13.918
But you've only used a little straw to fill up the water drinking from him. We've got to become bigger drinkers. Drink from the well.

00:17:13.919 --> 00:17:23.291
Just like he said, 'I'm opening the caps of revival of the deeper water.'Remember the word I gave you all? It was Brother Hagin.

00:17:23.292 --> 00:17:38.512
They took a little bit of a cup and they drank a little of it, and Oral Roberts had a little cup of that revival, and Kathryn Kuhlman and all the ones in the tent revivals back in the early 1900s, like Jack Coe and all them.

00:17:38.513 --> 00:17:47.822
But the Lord said to me, 'Brandon, where I'm taking the body of Christ in these last days is in the deeper water.

00:17:47.823 --> 00:18:13.519
And you will not just go ankle deep, but you're going to go all the way down.'Remember when I told you I went to the throne room and he said, 'It's time for the body to go over the head,'because there was a fountain of water flowing down at the Father's throne and there was ankle-deep water, waist-deep water, and all the way down.

00:18:13.520 --> 00:18:23.359
It was the clearest crystal water I've ever seen. The pool of living water was flowing out of the throne and out of the Father.

00:18:23.360 --> 00:18:36.797
And he said, "Brandon, it's time to go to the deeper waters."It's undignified, folks. It's losing yourself and not being dignified.

00:18:36.798 --> 00:18:44.159
It's being filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit for what he's wanting to do in these last days.

00:18:44.160 --> 00:18:51.043
Go to the deeper water where the Holy Ghost is at. Lose yourself in it.

00:18:51.044 --> 00:19:12.478
Not caring who's around you, dying to self—what we're always talking about—dying to self, being a vessel that God can use because you are filled and controlled by the Holy Spirit, being that river like Diana was talking about, getting to it and drinking.

00:19:12.479 --> 00:19:23.357
So, how do you drink, Diana? You have to open your mouth to drink, because you can be in a pool full of water and you can die of thirst if you don't open your mouth and drink, right?

00:19:23.358 --> 00:19:37.272
You can be all the way in that pool and totally die of thirst. You could be in ten-foot-deep water with your head all the way in it, but if you don't open your mouth and drink, you can die of thirst.

00:19:37.273 --> 00:19:44.049
You have to drink. Be a receiver. Receive. How do you receive?

00:19:44.050 --> 00:19:49.063
By singing hymns and spiritual songs, making melody in your heart unto the Lord.

00:19:49.064 --> 00:19:57.590
It's not about having the mightiest prayer; it's about being the biggest receiver, opening yourself up as he's pouring the rivers out.

00:19:57.591 --> 00:20:09.599
Just think, "I am just receiving."I'm going to be the biggest receiving vessel and let the rivers flow out of you.

00:20:09.600 --> 00:20:16.564
That's it. Not drinking a little Holy Spirit with a little straw, but lapping it up.

00:20:16.565 --> 00:20:23.143
How desperate are you? Like he's talking about the mighty men of war, I want to lap it up.

00:20:23.144 --> 00:20:28.843
I'm down on my hands and knees. When Jesus was watching, I could see the way the Father was looking.

00:20:28.844 --> 00:20:35.513
Jesus was up there and he was looking at the people in the church and he was watching who was going to be undignified.

00:20:35.514 --> 00:20:39.460
I mean, you try not to be undignified. You know what I'm saying?

00:20:39.461 --> 00:20:51.839
Like, who's just sold out to me and how they drink? How desperate are they for that water right now?

00:20:51.840 --> 00:21:00.519
My God, I'm desperate, folks. Diana is desperate. And I ain't going to drink through a little bitty straw looking for Jesus.

00:21:00.520 --> 00:21:15.056
I want him to be like Niagara Falls in New York. And I want to go up there and just sit underneath those falls and open my mouth as wide as I can even if it drowns me.

00:21:15.057 --> 00:21:22.099
Drown me, Lord. Drown me with your glory. Pour out your spirit on me, Father.

00:21:22.100 --> 00:21:26.715
We're thirsty. We're hungry. We're desperate. We need more of you.

00:21:26.716 --> 00:21:36.763
And even if we look stupid in the natural, let us do something big for you.

00:21:36.764 --> 00:21:45.643
I just think whenever that prayer time happened yesterday, I thought, "This cannot just go at the end of a session tonight.

00:21:45.644 --> 00:21:59.997
It has to be the whole primary focus for tomorrow."When Jesus showed me that yesterday, I sat there and I just went, "Wow, how desperate.

00:21:59.998 --> 00:22:06.290
How much water?"Because out of your belly shall flow rivers of living water.

00:22:06.291 --> 00:22:12.499
You have another scripture. Yeah, James 1:17-18. This is the Message version.

00:22:12.500 --> 00:22:21.053
It says, "So my very dear friends, don't get thrown off course. Every desirable and beneficial gift comes out of heaven.

00:22:21.054 --> 00:22:26.234
The gifts are rivers of light cascading down from the father of light.

00:22:26.235 --> 00:22:30.933
There is nothing deceitful in God, nothing two-faced, nothing fickle.

00:22:30.934 --> 00:22:41.698
He brought us to life using the true word, showing us off as the crown of all his creatures."It flows like a river.

00:22:41.699 --> 00:22:46.829
The gifts are rivers of light cascading down from the father of light.

00:22:46.830 --> 00:23:03.342
Glory to God. Folks, will you be used? Will you drink? Will you drink from his cup? Like I said, "Fill my cup, Lord. I lift it up, Lord.

00:23:03.343 --> 00:23:13.918
Come and quench this thirsting of my soul."As I say it all the time, I sing it to y'all because it's the bread of heaven.

00:23:13.919 --> 00:23:33.213
Feed me till I want no more. Fill my cup. Fill it up and make me whole—spirit, soul, and body.

00:23:33.214 --> 00:23:46.092
I can just see it in the vision again. The people who are just barely drinking, looking around.

00:23:46.093 --> 00:23:50.370
Versus the people who are radical. They dip in their hands. "Oh, I need more water.

00:23:50.371 --> 00:23:54.239
I need more water. I'm going deep."In fact, I'm jumping in and I'm going to have a splashdown.

00:23:54.240 --> 00:24:16.518
I'm going to get down in there and I'm going to drink all that water. And people are just freaking out. "I can use him.

00:24:16.519 --> 00:24:31.851
I can use her because they're just sold out."I'm watching the people and I'm watching to see how they drink.

00:24:31.852 --> 00:24:41.119
How are they drinking today? When I first saw it when I was praying, I thought, "Well, what does that matter?

00:24:41.120 --> 00:25:02.798
What do you mean, I'm watching to see how they drink?"I pondered that and I prayed over that and I thought, "Isn't that interesting?"And then the Lord gave me these scriptures and it's just amazing to me.

00:25:02.799 --> 00:25:18.935
He so desires for everybody to be like David when he danced out of his robe because his wife was looking up at him and going, "This guy has lost it."But he was sold out.

00:25:18.936 --> 00:25:23.686
He was dancing before the Lord and he danced himself right out of his clothes.

00:25:23.687 --> 00:25:28.373
It was a Holy Ghost dance. Obviously, it wasn't in the flesh.

00:25:28.374 --> 00:25:41.240
He was just sold out. I don't advise that, but I'm just saying being sold out. How desperate, how hungry, how thirsty are you?

00:25:41.241 --> 00:25:48.404
Drinking not from a straw, but standing underneath that massive waterfall.

00:25:48.405 --> 00:25:56.394
Drink, drink, drink. And how you drink is you pray in the spirit and you pray in tongues.

00:25:56.395 --> 00:26:06.317
And as you pray, you're drinking. You're drawing from that well. The Holy Spirit is drawing from the well out of your belly.

00:26:06.318 --> 00:26:16.312
You're drawing it and it's flowing out of you, but you're drinking and the water is like a recycle.

00:26:16.313 --> 00:26:24.873
It comes in and it goes out. But the bigger you drink, the more the whole waterfall comes out of you.

00:26:24.874 --> 00:26:35.754
And if you don't, you'll get dry. You don't want to get dry. You have to be filled.

00:26:35.755 --> 00:26:43.961
